data.description: Updated ranch home with fenced in yard and 2 garages. The first floor has two bedrooms, a large living room with a built-in bookshelf, kitchen, and bathroom. The basement is finished with two bedrooms, full bathroom, family room, and laundry/utility room. The home has an attached garage and breezeway. The home also has a detached garage with an attached carport. Attached to the back of the home is a large covered patio. Part of the backyard is fenced in.
